name: oOoOO
description: '''oOoOO''' (pronounced "oh") is an American [[witch house (music genre)|witch house]]/[[chillwave]] project led by Christopher Dexter Greenspan. The project was founded in 2008. Along with [[White Ring (band)|White Ring]] and [[Salem (Michigan band)|Salem]], oOoOO is often recognized as a pioneer of the witch house sound.
